SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4625
| summarize Attempts=count(), arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by Account
| project
TimeGenerated,
Account,
AccountType,
EventID,
Activity,
IpAddress,
Attempts
| order by TimeGenerated desc

Displays only the latest failed authentication attempt for each account while also showing the total number of attempts made against that account.
This provides a concise view of recent attacker activity without displaying duplicate log entries.
